title: Motorcycle crash closes part of Highway 63
text:
The crash happened just after 8:30 Monday night. It happened in the northbound lanes of Highway 63, just south of Route AC (Grindstone Parkway). One northbound lane is closed. 
We'll post more information as soon as it's available.
